{
    "title": "小麦：地球上最重要的谷物",
    "description": "小麦是一种谷物，属于禾本科植物，生长于世界各地的温带地区",
    "images": ["https://i.ibb.co/8bvJRmw/wheat-blog.jpg"],
    "structure": [
        {
            "contentType": "header",
            "content": "小麦：地球上最重要的谷物",
            "address": {
                "authorPicture": "https://flowbite.com/docs/images/people/profile-picture-2.jpg",
